How is my father?

377
01:02:37,947 --> 01:02:39,032
How is His Majesty?

378
01:02:40,824 --> 01:02:41,700
Report!

379
01:02:41,825 --> 01:02:44,787
General Nangong has returned
with important intelligence.

380
01:03:01,511 --> 01:03:02,429
Well,

381
01:03:02,804 --> 01:03:04,180
how is His Majesty?

382
