General,

384
01:03:11,854 --> 01:03:13,272
the Immortal Pill is ready.

385
01:03:13,439 --> 01:03:17,151
On his way back,
General Xu was ambushed by rebels.

386
01:03:19,403 --> 01:03:20,778
Prepare the troops for departure.

387
01:03:20,862 --> 01:03:21,738
Yes, sir.

388
01:03:22,281 --> 01:03:23,865
- Fresh horses!
- Yes sir!

389
