Father had too many
people around him.

395
01:03:51,350 --> 01:03:52,601
I fear for our plans.

396
01:03:53,102 --> 01:03:55,604
The concubines are ready
to be entombed with him.

397
01:04:05,572 --> 01:04:07,698
Your Majesty, the Immortal Pill is ready,

398
01:04:07,782 --> 01:04:09,699
but was taken in a rebel ambush.

399
01:04:09,784 --> 01:04:11,994
Your servant begs leave
to go retrieve it forthwith!

400
01:04:12,078 --> 01:04:14,497
General Meng,
your duty is His Majesty's safety.

401
01:04:15,038 --> 01:04:16,290
You should stay.

402
01:04:18,000 --> 01:04:19,668
The situation is most urgent!

403
01:04:20,293 --> 01:04:21,795
I await His Majesty's orders.

404
01:04:27,300 --> 01:04:31,721
His Majesty commands you
to retrieve the pill.

405
01:04:32,555 --> 01:04:34,015
- As ordered!
- Wait.

406
01:04:35,099 --> 01:04:39,729
His Majesty has few troops
in his entourage.

407
01:04:40,605 --> 01:04:43,650
If you go all out for the pill,

408
01:04:43,775 --> 01:04:45,985
and the rebels strike,

409
01:04:46,277 --> 01:04:48,737
I fear for His Majesty's safety.

410
01:04:49,613 --> 01:04:54,493
In that case,
I'll only take the Light Cavalry.

411
01:05:03,293 --> 01:05:04,878
I won't tell.

412
01:05:05,628 --> 01:05:07,713
His Majesty still needs treatment.

413
01:05:08,339 --> 01:05:09,882
Let me try once more.

414
01:05:22,687 --> 01:05:23,645
General Meng Yi!

415
01:05:31,195 --> 01:05:32,362
Farewell, Your Highness.

416
01:05:33,196 --> 01:05:34,531
You must come back.

417
01:05:36,908 --> 01:05:38,827
The pill can save His Majesty's life,

418
01:05:39,160 --> 01:05:40,620
and therefore yours too.

419
01:05:43,539 --> 01:05:46,250
Know that my heart
is yours forever.

420
01:06:02,850 --> 01:06:04,267
I await your return.

421
01:06:08,688 --> 01:06:10,398
Attention, soldiers of the Meng clan!

422
01:06:10,898 --> 01:06:12,442
Those with aged parents are excused!

423
01:06:15,069 --> 01:06:16,320
The only sons are excused!

424
01:06:21,868 --> 01:06:23,369
Husbands and fathers are excused!

425
01:06:27,248 --> 01:06:30,166
Those who are excused, guard the camp!
The rest of you, mount!

426
01:06:34,755 --> 01:06:35,797
General!

427
01:06:37,257 --> 01:06:38,884
How many years
have we shared our honor?

428
01:06:39,300 --> 01:06:41,469
Why can we not
live and die together now?

429
01:06:44,097 --> 01:06:47,099
I, Nangong Yan swears to follow you
even unto death!

