436
01:08:54,720 --> 01:08:56,972
I have orders from the Chancellor
to take the pill.

437
01:08:57,181 --> 01:09:00,934
Failure to hand it over
is disobedience, Xu Gui!

438
01:09:01,644 --> 01:09:04,104
I can only give the Pill

439
01:09:04,980 --> 01:09:06,565
to General Meng.

440
01:09:07,274 --> 01:09:08,817
I won't give to anyone else!

441
01:09:23,247 --> 01:09:25,708
The Chancellor bears
His Majesty's word.

442
01:09:26,292 --> 01:09:27,877
Obey right now!

