Prepare to attack!

446
01:09:48,604 --> 01:09:49,647
Defenses!

447
01:09:57,863 --> 01:09:59,615
Ready archers!

448
01:10:10,042 --> 01:10:10,792
Fire!

449
01:10:19,468 --> 01:10:20,677
Charge!

450
01:10:32,063 --> 01:10:33,314
Attack!

451
01:11:30,535 --> 01:11:33,871
Zhao Kuang, His Majesty orders!
Yield at once!

452
01:11:35,831 --> 01:11:38,125
You dare fake
an Imperial Decree?

453
01:11:39,752 --> 01:11:40,961
General Meng?

454
01:11:42,838 --> 01:11:44,131
Leave no one alive!

455
01:11:48,468 --> 01:11:49,803
General Zhao!

456
01:11:50,094 --> 01:11:51,721
General Meng comes
with an Imperial Decree!

457
01:11:52,305 --> 01:11:53,932
Why do you disobey?

458
01:11:54,641 --> 01:11:57,393
Your disobedience in the field
will be punished! Attack!

459
01:12:11,156 --> 01:12:12,115
Soldiers at the back!

460
01:12:12,533 --> 01:12:14,785
No one moves without my orders!

