692
01:45:39,350 --> 01:45:41,518
Where's the Qin Emperor's sarcophagus?

693
01:45:48,149 --> 01:45:49,818
It must be in the Celestial Palace.

694
01:45:55,031 --> 01:45:56,825
Take me there! Take me there!

695
01:46:06,250 --> 01:46:07,126
Stay where you are!

696
01:46:08,127 --> 01:46:10,087
Don't you dare try
to steal anything

697
01:46:10,295 --> 01:46:11,463
or take her away!

698
01:46:12,297 --> 01:46:13,883
That depends on
whether you can stop me.

699
01:47:21,697 --> 01:47:24,533
Don't worry.
I won't let anyone hurt you.

700
01:47:47,722 --> 01:47:50,099
Jack! Help me!

701
01:48:03,903 --> 01:48:06,697
Ok Soo, I'll take you
away from here.

702
01:48:14,455 --> 01:48:15,498
Let's go.

703
01:48:38,060 --> 01:48:39,103
Jack!

704
01:48:39,854 --> 01:48:40,730
William!

705
01:48:42,231 --> 01:48:43,733
- William!
- Help me!

706
01:48:47,861 --> 01:48:48,945
Hang on to me!

707
01:48:49,321 --> 01:48:50,739
I only do scientific research.

708
01:48:51,657 --> 01:48:52,949
I'm no tomb raider.

709
01:48:56,202 --> 01:48:57,328
Jack...

710
01:49:00,498 --> 01:49:02,417
you must get out no matter what,

711
01:49:02,751 --> 01:49:04,544
and finish my research.

712
01:49:09,090 --> 01:49:10,133
Jack.

713
01:49:14,136 --> 01:49:16,597
Jack, are we still friends?

714
01:49:30,485 --> 01:49:31,486
Jack?

715
01:49:35,031 --> 01:49:36,866
You really aren't Meng Yi.

716
01:49:40,704 --> 01:49:41,745
No, I'm not.

717
01:49:45,541 --> 01:49:47,168
Whether I'm Meng Yi or not
doesn't matter.

718
01:49:47,335 --> 01:49:49,212
What matters is that
we leave here now!

719
01:49:50,921 --> 01:49:52,381
You're not Meng Yi.

720
01:49:54,091 --> 01:49:55,593
I'm not leaving.

721
01:49:56,259 --> 01:49:57,886
I'll await Meng Yi's return.

722
01:49:59,387 --> 01:50:00,931
Ok Soo, hurry! There's no time!

723
01:50:01,723 --> 01:50:04,101
No. He's not dead.

724
01:50:04,934 --> 01:50:06,311
I'll wait for him.

725
01:50:06,728 --> 01:50:07,729
Ok Soo!

726
01:50:08,980 --> 01:50:10,022
Ok Soo!

727
01:50:55,149 --> 01:50:57,234
At last! Immortality!

728
01:56:06,235 --> 01:56:07,361
General Zhao!

729
01:56:07,861 --> 01:56:09,572
General Meng comes
with an Imperial Decree!

730
01:56:10,155 --> 01:56:11,657
Why do you disobey?

731
01:56:12,407 --> 01:56:14,034
The emperor is dead now,

732
01:56:14,618 --> 01:56:15,786
and you have to...

733
01:56:17,079 --> 01:56:18,080
From now on,

734
01:56:19,206 --> 01:56:20,373
we will never...

735
01:56:21,874 --> 01:56:24,169
Oh, no!

736
01:56:25,170 --> 01:56:27,839
That last line... the last line!

737
01:56:28,130 --> 01:56:29,131
From now on,

738
01:56:30,007 --> 01:56:32,051
we will never separate again.

739
01:56:39,183 --> 01:56:40,267
You've been lying to me!

740
01:56:41,560 --> 01:56:44,563
From beginning to end,
from today onwards...

741
01:56:45,272 --> 01:56:47,899
You have been
speaking Cantonese style Mandarin

742
01:56:47,983 --> 01:56:50,110
from beginning to end.

